{"tid":2309041,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"大家估下幾時會有支那疫苗包裝成英美疫苗供貨香港","createTime":"2020-12-02T09:30:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T13:37:17.000Z","uid":70786,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"5e30d4d493e114bef4e9cd21cf49e7600adbad8d","tid":2309041,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T09:30:58.000Z","msg":"雖然支那疫苗本身都六百幾人仔<br />\n但係香港人消費力咁高又咁抗拒支那疫苗<br />\n實好多人非英美疫苗不打<br />\n只要將支那疫苗包裝成英美疫苗<br />\n一劑賣貴一兩倍都唔成問題<br />\n到時私家診所又排長龍，排隊打HPV疫苗咁嘅墟冚場面又再重現<br />\n因為要幫國家散貨，海關隻眼開隻眼閉<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/mask.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府再仆街d就將接種「英美疫苗」紀錄綁定安心出行app<br />\n打過就有特權<br />\n出街唔使戴口罩<br />\n出入任何地方都通行無阻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84535c99db4b90ae6a9ef6620f23ab8f7fb3299f","tid":2309041,"uid":70786,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T09:34:26.000Z","msg":"到時連傳媒監察嘅功能都失去埋<br />\n以前就可以直接向英美疫苗商求證有冇供貨俾某診所<br />\n今時今日唔會再有專題報導踢爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e24d7b27898a7d9deada7b4fe95f108485464964","tid":2309041,"uid":63311,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T09:35:01.000Z","msg":"讓官員警察先打！"},{"pid":"e41d40f0385fd013803c21d98dc7bd6fdaba4f71","tid":2309041,"uid":185656,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T09:35:14.000Z","msg":"第一步會扮土炮先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccccc07d8842c12698cc890e12196484d9278cde","tid":2309041,"uid":138964,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T09:36:29.000Z","msg":"以前記者仲可以掲露真相<br />\n俾市民知道當中包含左啲乜<br />\n越黎越似 支那疫苗打死人 上訪無門一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇市民條命夠唔夠彩數"},{"pid":"f0ee82d1f1c5401b174fde6549493c008e215759","tid":2309041,"uid":211466,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T09:38:53.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">建議全世界唔好供俾香港</span><br />\n<br />\n俾大